HEADWORD: Rathe
<hw>Rathe</hw> }</mhw> <pr>(r⟦acr⟧th)</pr>,
<pos>a.</pos> <ety>[AS. <ets>hr⟦ae⟧⟦edh⟧</ets>, <ets>hr⟦ae⟧d</ets>,
